# Spec-driven development

- **Source of truth:** `docs/SPEC.md` (section numbers are stable references in commits and PRs).
- **Requirement changes:** Edit the spec first — see `.cursor/skills/sdd-spec-change-first/SKILL.md`.
- **Implementation:** Domain/UI — `.cursor/skills/spec-driven-financial-planner/SKILL.md`.
- **Tests & goldens:** `.cursor/skills/sdd-verify-with-tests/SKILL.md` (Vitest, §10, `src/test/fixtures/`).
- **Commits / PRs:** `.cursor/skills/sdd-commit-and-review/SKILL.md`.
- **Non-goals:** Do not implement §11 items without first updating `docs/SPEC.md` (and `README.md` if user-facing defaults change).
